ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

The following novel techniques documented in this repository are original
work by Stelliro and require attribution when used:

  - Sparse Voxel Radiance Marching (SVRM) with Depth-Gap Bridging
  - GTAO+ Dual-Horizon Multi-Scale AO with Bent Normals
  - Camera-Ray Shadow Segmentation for World-Anchored Volumetrics
  - Orientation Anchor System (6-Point Surface Capture)
  - Biome-Aware Per-Pixel Lighting Profiles
  - Hybrid Forward+Compute Pipeline Architecture

Built with the Vulkan graphics API (https://www.vulkan.org/) by Khronos Group.
